title: Sabrina Eisenberg
text: I am a PhD student in the University of South Florida’s CNS Psychology program. I specialize in social psychology and I’m interested in mystical experiences, religiosity, and close relationships. In my downtime, I enjoy spending time in nature, drawing, and exploring Tampa.
